# Install Nickel compiler and language server:
#
# - download from https://github.com/tweag/nickel/releases :
#   - nickel-x86_64-linux and
#   - nls-x86_64-linux
# - move them to ~/bin
# - make them executable:
chmod +x nickel-x86_64-linux nls-x86_64-linux
# - create simlinks:
ln -s nickel-x86_64-linux nickel
ln -s nls-x86_64-linux nls

